      "description": "This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between a well-loved daily driver and a meticulously maintained machine. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though a close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side wheel arch\u2014typical signs of careful road use. Inside, the cabin is smoke-free and remarkably clean; the premium leather seats remain supple, showing only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every button, switch, and digital display functions exactly as intended, including the dual-zone climate control and the premium audio system. Mechanically, this car is turn-key ready. It has a documented service history, including a recent full synthetic oil change and a brake fluid flush performed last month. The tires provide excellent grip with approximately 70% tread remaining, and the transmission shifts smoothly through every gear without hesitation. This is a reliable, high-performing vehicle that has been treated with respect and is ready for its next chapter.",
